te-for-outdoor-swansea-show-2893188">在斯旺西的辛格尔顿公园</a>和沃灵顿的 Neighborhood Weekender 进行了两场户外演出后，就没有再一起演出过。那时，两人分手的传闻已经沸沸扬扬。</p><p>他们已经预订了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2024-festival-confirm-day-splits-and-whos-headlining-when-3548999">今年在雷丁和利兹的头条新闻，</a>他们将在周五在利兹和周日在雷丁演出。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/LIAM-GALLAGHER">Liam Gallagher</a>也是当天音乐节的头条新闻，而其余的头条新闻则由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/BLINK-182">Blink-182</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gerry-cinnamon">Gerry Cinnamon</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/FRED-AGAIN">Fred Again..</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana Del Rey 占据。</a></p><p> Catfish 和 Bottlemen 即将宣布的现场表演将是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-and-the-bottlemen-bondy-says-he-left-the-band-last-year-3240536">吉他手约翰尼·“邦迪”·邦德</a>离开后的首次现场表演。</p><p> 2022 年，邦德证实他已于前一年离开乐队，声称阵容的变化和乐队未来的不确定性源于“我发现无法忍受的行为不断重复发生”。</p><p> “简单地说，我觉得职业和个人关系都完全失调了，”他在声明中补充道。</p><p>邦迪接着解释说，去年他作为会议音乐家与乐队一起演奏了四场夏季演出，“因为没有其他人准备这样做”。</p><p> “从那时起（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/neighbourhood-weekender-rescheduled-2021-festival-2676869">Neighborhood Festival &#39;21</a> ），我与其余乐队成员没有任何形式的联系或联系，”他写道。他补充说，他“假设”乐队会通知歌迷他以及鼓手鲍勃·霍尔的离开，但“据我所知，这还没有发生”。</p><p> Catfish and the Bottlemen 的上一张专辑是 2019 年的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/catfish-and-the-bottlemen-the-balance-review-2480270#:~:text=There%20are%20solid%20pop%2Drock,had%20a%20one%2Doff%20tune.">The Balance</a> 》。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-and-the-bottlemen-post-clip-of-first-new-music-in-five-years-3589012">五年来第一首新音乐的《Catfish and the Bottlemen》帖子剪辑</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
乔丹·诺斯 (Jordan North) 对他离开第一广播电台的评论：“我很快就会回来” https://www.nme.com/news/music/jordan-north-comments-on-his-departure-from-radio-1-ill-be-back-soon-3589008?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=jordan-北方关于他离开第一广播电台的评论 - 很快就会回来Alex RigottiSat, 17 Feb 2024 13:15:13 +0000 Music NewsNewsBBCRadio 1 https://www.nme.com/?p=3589008 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Jordan-North-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="乔丹·北（Joe Maher/Getty Images 拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Jordan-North-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Jordan-North-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Jordan-North-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Jordan-North-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Jordan-North-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Jordan-North-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在他即将接替的杰米·莱恩(Jamie Laing)引发争议之际，突然宣布退出</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jordan-north-comments-on-his-departure-from-radio-1-ill-be-back-soon-3589008">乔丹·诺斯 (Jordan North) 评论他离开第一广播台的帖子：“我很快就会回来”，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Jordan-North-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="乔丹·北（Joe Maher/Getty Images 拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Jordan-North-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Jordan-North-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Jordan-North-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Jordan-North-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Jordan-North-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Jordan-North-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乔丹·诺斯 (Jordan North) 正式宣布退出<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/radio-1">BBC 广播 1 台。</a></p><p>昨天，BBC <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jordan-north-to-leave-bbc-radio-1-after-10-years-to-be-replaced-by-jamie-laing-3588687">宣布兰开夏郡主持人在工作十年后将离开该电台</a>。自 2021 年以来，他一直与 Vick Hope 一起主持驾车节目以及车站的其他节目。</p><p>现在，诺斯在社交媒体上分享了他自己关于这一令人震惊的举动的声明，并分享了他在第一广播电台工作期间的一系列照片。“我只是想借此机会感谢第一广播电台所有出色的同事/才华横溢的制作人许多我认为是终生的朋友并且会非常想念的人，在过去的 24 小时里你们都联系了我，这确实意味着很多，”他写道。</p><p>这位伯恩利的主持人接着感谢了众多 BBC 广播 1 台的主持人，他说：“对于我那些出色的主持人同事，我希望我能亲自感谢你们所有人，我很喜欢与你们一起工作，这绝对是一场爆炸！”他还特别向“我的犯罪搭档维克·霍普（Vick Hope）致敬……我会怀念每天和你一起播出的时光。”诺斯接着“最重要的是”感谢他的节目的许多听众：“你们的善意话语和信息非常可爱，非常感谢。”</p><p> “我很快就会回来，迫不及待地想再次见到你们。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C3ciIrhIauv/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http